Encoding considerations : binary

Interoperability considerations : none

Published specification : This MIME type is described fully in ETSI 
   TS 102 832: "Digital Video Broadcasting (DVB); IP Datacast over 
   DVB-H: Notification Framework", which is available at 
   http://www.etsi.org/

Applications which use this media : This media type is used by 
   Notification Applications to initialize the consumption of 
   Notifications.
